"      Stress-induced (takotsubo) cardiomyopathy",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?38/38/39530?source=related_link\">",
"      Troponins and creatine kinase as biomarkers of cardiac injury",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
